{"tid":1050286,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法國擬開徵數碼稅　阻大型科企避稅","createTime":"2019-03-06T23:24:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T04:25:46.000Z","uid":141151,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1bcf6361a12a13f2be3aa3006a35b022afe5d535","tid":1050286,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T23:24:29.000Z","msg":"法國擬開徵數碼稅　阻大型科企避稅<br />\n<br />\n法國政府周三（6日）公布計劃，向Google、Facebook等科技公司加徵3%數碼稅，阻止大型科企避稅。<br />\n<br />\n法新社報道，由於愛爾蘭等稅率較低的國家反對，加上擔心激怒美國總統特朗普，法國總統馬克龍（Emmanuel Macron）未能說服歐洲盟國共同行動，故只好單獨向全球網路巨擘「開刀」。<br />\n<br />\n根據即將送交內閣討論和國會審查通過的方案，法國將向在當地營運的大型網路公司徵收3%數碼稅，在全球收入超過7.5億歐元（約66.6億港元），而在法國收入至少達2500萬歐元（約2.22億港元）的網路公司，都要繳交數碼稅。勒梅爾表示，倘若未達這兩項標準，將毋須繳交數碼稅。<br />\n<br />\n法國財長勒梅爾（Bruno Le Maire）向《巴黎人報》（Le Parisien）表示，於2019年加徵數碼稅後，本年度新增稅收將達5億歐元（約44.4億港元），同時稅收將快速增長。<br />\n<br />\n勒梅爾說，大約30家來自美國、中國、德國、西班牙、英國，還有法國的網路公司會受到影響，主要受影響公司為使用顧客資料出售網上廣告的公司，另外亦包括網上服務公司如Airbnb和Uber，而直接於網上出售商品的公司則不受影響。他指出，此舉關乎「財稅正義」，並指「這些網路公司所繳的稅比歐洲中小企業少14%」。"},{"pid":"9b031f64d0e0d5c25d446bed57a4e9c10d5f1b7e","tid":1050286,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T23:53:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97aaa7fd89584d7b41a0da880f7effe3b64bb633","tid":1050286,"uid":121146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T00:16:28.000Z","msg":"法國佬到底窮成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f4dca8827d993997a5cf944f8dffcf2a85208fe","tid":1050286,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T00:18:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09494a7222579f1966e9edfd1f4c80dce8cea11a","tid":1050286,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f4dca8827d993997a5cf944f8dffcf2a85208fe","tid":1050286,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T00:18:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T01:37:30.000Z","msg":"返少d工，上多d網<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc30dc117e678f98cc2b3f77cdd64762b6b36a00","tid":1050286,"uid":45332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T01:56:21.000Z","msg":"法國佬自己間OVH呢?"},{"pid":"702dacdc30e7bd4731354648b79d7ccaf286ee2e","tid":1050286,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T03:51:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1bdb02e1d3532309dd1f5e73178e8f9b2342582","tid":1050286,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T04:25:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}